result.arabic_text: قَالَ رَبِّ إِنِّي لَآ أَمۡلِكُ إِلَّا نَفۡسِي وَأَخِيۖ فَٱفۡرُقۡ بَيۡنَنَا وَبَيۡنَ ٱلۡقَوۡمِ ٱلۡفَٰسِقِينَ
result.translation: 25. Nabii Muusa isi Rabbi kallacak Yi-Rabbow diggah anu inni Nafsii kee inni toobokoyta Nabii Haaruun nafsik-sa duudam mayyuk nee kee Ni-maray ku-amri cineeh ku- taaqatak yewqê fan baxisaay nee mekel iyye.
